      "utterance": "对，Wallet会发两个请求：首先是Request tweaks & UTXOs for block，带上业务标识Retail_CustomerLoyalty；然后是Request filters获取GCS过滤器。Oracle分别返回Tweaks & relevant UTXOs和utxo and outpoint filters。",
